Cara penggunaan Css
Memisahkan Style Css dengan html untuk dapat digunakan kembali di fila yang lain
 exmp :

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Document</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="asset/css/app.css"> (file ini dipishakan di folder format Css)
</head>
<body>
    <h1>Tutorial Css</h1>

    <h2>Tutorial Css</h2>

    <p>Elements in HTML have attributes. These are additional values that configure the elements or adjust their behavior in various ways.</p>
</body>
</html>


File Css :

*{
    background-color: bisque;
}
 
h1{
    color: #18ef0cf6;
    font-size: 200%;
}
h2{
    color: #1348e9f6;
    text-decoration: underline;
}
p{
    text-align: justify;
    font-weight: 200;
    line-height: 1;
}
